			<CASNumber>6484-52-2</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Ammonium nitrate is a chemical compound used predominantly in agriculture as a high-nitrogen fertilizer. It is also used as an oxidizing agent in explosives for mining, quarrying, and civil construction purposes. Its production involves the neutralization of nitric acid with ammonia, followed by crystallization. Ammonium nitrate is available to consumers and often found in granulated form. It is commonly used as part of a production mix for formulations that deliver nutrients to crops.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">硝酸铵是一种化学化合物，主要用在农业中作为含氮量高的肥料。它也被用作开采、采石和民用建筑爆破的氧化剂。其生产包括中和硝酸与氨，随后进行结晶。硝酸铵对消费者而言是可获得的，通常以颗粒形式存在。它常作为提供作物养分的生产混合配方的一部分。</common:generalComment>
